  "content_markdown": "1\n\n###  Application and Definition\n\n1.1\n\nUnless otherwise stated, this Part applies only to:\n\n  1. (1) [deleted.]\n  2. (2) a _third country firm._\n  3. that is:\n  4. (3) a _bank_ ; or\n  5. (4) a _designated investment firm._\n\n*Effective: 31/12/2020*\n\n1.2\n\nIn this Part the following definition shall apply:\n\n_resolution plan\n\n_\n\nmeans, in relation to a _firm_ , the plan for the resolution of the _firm_ prepared by the authority in the jurisdiction of the _firm’s_ head office responsible for the _firm’s_ resolution.\n\n*Effective: 05/09/2014*\n\n2\n\n###  Adequacy of Resolution Plan\n\n2.1\n\nThis chapter applies only to a _third country firm_ that is:\n\n  1. (1) a _bank_ ; or\n  2. (2) a _designated investment firm_.\n\n*Effective: 05/09/2014*\n\n2.2\n\nA _firm_ must take all steps within its control to ensure that its _resolution plan_ provides adequately for the resolution of the _firm’s UK_ branch.\n\n*Effective: 05/09/2014*\n\n3\n\n###  Branch Return\n\n3.1\n\n[Deleted.]\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2020*\n\n4\n\n###  Form\n\n4.1\n\n[Deleted.]\n\n*Effective: 01/01/2020*",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"col9\">\n<div class=\"clear\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"part-content\">\n\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"7c700a257d6f47a89187fe03cfdf7119\" id=\"7e247e0f5827493cb7f4d2c4c4e9097a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t1\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tApplication and Definition\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"80760692566a4f1c93e4ba6e25a6a39d\" id=\"949c4dfbb4c1426fb5d0567fadf69c7b\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>Unless otherwise stated, this Part applies only to:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) [deleted.]</li>\n<li>(2) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52382\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-60bfedb1b06645aeaf51d70560dbaa58\" title=\"third country firm\">third country firm</a>.</em></li>\n<li>that is:</li>\n<li>(3) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52212\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a63b910853324ee39842cfeceb781496\" title=\"bank\">bank</a></em>; or</li>\n<li>(4) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52381\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-4980ae28057640c1865355e3e0407e07\" title=\"designated investment firm\">designated investment firm</a>.</em></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/third-country-firms/05-09-2014#949c4dfbb4c1426fb5d0567fadf69c7b\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 1.1 before 31/12/2020\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"519ad5f85f4e46a386ed35cc29b93bfd\" id=\"e5316abc90914cf68a0629cf41fab9e5\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t1.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<div data-canvas-width=\"79.36460000000001\">In this Part the following definition shall apply:<br/><br/></div>\n<div data-canvas-width=\"108.16560000000001\"><em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52549\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-6378ba990b1640afb205b28e5757347f\" title=\"resolution plan\">resolution plan</a><br/><br/></em></div>\n<div data-canvas-width=\"168.34060000000002\" style=\"padding-left: 30px;\">means, in relation to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em>, the plan for the resolution of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> prepared by the authority in the jurisdiction of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm’s\">firm’s</a></em> head office responsible for the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm’s\">firm’s</a></em> resolution.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t05/09/2014\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"c4d107a37d344054a036df7bb437f6c3\" id=\"36ce0292b333448480b43905a2606cf6\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t2\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tAdequacy of Resolution Plan\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"ef2022fc0395447baf295bdd9989cc8c\" id=\"71025e0ac3b443b297ed7ba158208f3c\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"1\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>This chapter applies only to a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52382\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-60bfedb1b06645aeaf51d70560dbaa58\" title=\"third country firm\">third country firm</a></em> that is:</p>\n<ol class=\"new-bullet\">\n<li>(1) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52212\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-a63b910853324ee39842cfeceb781496\" title=\"bank\">bank</a></em>; or</li>\n<li>(2) a <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52381\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-4980ae28057640c1865355e3e0407e07\" title=\"designated investment firm\">designated investment firm</a></em>.</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t05/09/2014\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"f1e6b95fb73543d1b0e2126f80f99e53\" id=\"50f9e67de494437b9ff72bf58857a531\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t2.2\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<div>A <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm\">firm</a></em> must take all steps within its control to ensure that its <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52549\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-6378ba990b1640afb205b28e5757347f\" title=\"resolution plan\">resolution plan</a></em> provides adequately for the resolution of the <em><a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52114\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-c8c2638afbfe4ec2a4d936a5d365917f\" title=\"firm’s\">firm’s</a> <a class=\"glossary-link\" data-glossary-id=\"52122\" data-mce-linktype=\"2\" href=\"#glossary-term-f7844a8cbb824a52a26c043e3f6b584e\" title=\"UK\">UK</a></em> branch.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t05/09/2014\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"281b736d2c2d49d28518953698a5fb6b\" id=\"e21d4a686c184061b444888849da036a\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t3\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tBranch Return\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"785c96ca5e904a078f33265245d0882b\" id=\"069728c5d7bb4a569646e1744ea36c5b\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t3.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>[Deleted.]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2020\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/third-country-firms/01-07-2015#069728c5d7bb4a569646e1744ea36c5b\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 3.1 before 01/01/2020\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"chapter-section\" data-version=\"844ff014e7074612a14a57f2f473c128\" id=\"0d663d33062b4862a0976a9e6d71b173\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number rule-number--mega chapter-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t4\r\n\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<h3 class=\"header-sans chapter-heading\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\tForm\r\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block row-block--border\" data-version=\"20dc840034494f80bce7ce88681da749\" id=\"1d2159c92cbe4fa1afac090c83b4f405\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n<div class=\"div-row\" data-application-provision=\"0\">\n<div class=\"div-row__col-1\">\n<p>\n<span class=\"rule-number\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t4.1\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"div-row__col-2\">\n<p>[Deleted.]</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-block__info\">\n<ul class=\"list-links\">\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t01/01/2020\r\n\t\t\t\t</li>\n<li class=\"list-links__item\">\n<a class=\"list-links__link icon-previous\" href=\"/pra-rules/third-country-firms/01-01-2019#1d2159c92cbe4fa1afac090c83b4f405\">\r\n\t\t\tPast\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"visually-hidden\">\r\n\t\t\t\tversion of 4.1 before 01/01/2020\r\n\t\t\t</span>\n</a>\n</li>\n\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"page-utilities page-utilities--bg-grey\">\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div></div>\n</div>",
